sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    C->>B: POST /api/auth/refresh
    B->>B: SHA-256 hash token

    B->>DB: Find token by hash
    DB-->>B: Token record

    alt Not found or expired
        B-->>C: 401 Token Expired
    end

    alt Already revoked
        Note over B,DB: Replay attack detected
        B->>DB: Revoke all user tokens
        B-->>C: 401 Force re-login
    end

    B->>DB: Revoke old token
    B->>B: Sign new access token
    B->>B: Generate new refresh token
    B->>DB: Store new token
    B-->>C: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken}
